Method Detail

setChunks

void setChunks(gnu.trove.TIntArrayList chunks)
Sets the LF chunks to which this LF belongs. LF chunks are used during realization to ensure that certain edges are semantically complete before combination is attempted with edges with semantics outside the chunk. The chunks are numbered starting with 0, and null represents no chunks.
